{
  "stem": "2074.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had our own home and the land.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were comfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were there, at any point, anti-Jewish actions in your community that-- that made you start to realize what was about to come?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, the-- oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We felt it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew what went down, what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And oh, just-- sure, there were-- there were-- after World War I, some of them during World War I, a lot of Ukrainians went out of there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the war settled there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to deep Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After they came back after the war to their homes, then they finally started picking a little more on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and the matter of fact that one family-- my parents still [INAUDIBLE] while they were rebuilding their home that was damaged during the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their sons captured my mother and father during the hiding as I'll tell you later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were hiding 15 months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they walked out one night to ask for bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somebody told on them, and he sat on a horse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was at the winter time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother and father were running barefooted on the snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And according to the foot marks in the snow, the-- that guy who grew up in our house, a favor for nothing, captured my mother- turned very Nazi, captured my mother and father in the woods sitting under a tree barefooted and was driving them back to be killed.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they brought them to-- and after 15 months of hiding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what-- 1941, June 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, 1939, the Russians and the Germans divided up-- divided up the country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was part Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Near the Bug River, they made a border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came under the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
